      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">53.236-1</ph> Construction.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The following forms are prescribed, as stated below, for use in contracting for construction, alteration, or repair, or dismantling, demolition, or removal of improvements.</p>
         <ol id="d3804e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e22">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            [Reserved]</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e27">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitation-offer-and-award-construction-alteration-or-repair"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref "> SF 1442</xref> (Rev. 12/2022.),  <i>Solicitation, Offer and Award (Construction, Alteration, or Repair)</i>. <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitation-offer-and-award-construction-alteration-or-repair"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 1442</xref> is prescribed for use in soliciting offers and awarding contracts expected to exceed the simplified acquisition threshold for-</p>
               <ol id="d3804e62" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e40">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Construction, alteration, or repair; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e45">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Dismantling, demolition, or removal of improvements (and may be used for contracts within the simplified acquisition threshold), as specified in <xref href="36.701.dita#FAR_36_701"
                              base="i1078213"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">36.701</xref>(a).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e53">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                     <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/order-supplies-and-services-0"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref "> OF 347</xref> (Rev.2/2012), Order for Supplies or Services</i>. <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/order-supplies-and-services-0"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">OF 347</xref>, prescribed in <xref href="53.213.dita#FAR_53_213"
                        base="i1001023"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">53.213</xref>(f) (or an approved agency form), may be used for contracts under the simplified acquisition threshold for-</p>
               <ol id="d3804e107" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e69">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Construction, alteration, or repair; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e74">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Dismantling, demolition, or removal of improvements, as specified in <xref href="36.701.dita#FAR_36_701"
                              base="i1078213"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">36.701</xref>(b).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d3850e82">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">
                     <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/abstract-offers-construction"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref "> OF 1419</xref>(11/88Ed.), Abstract of Offers-Construction, and <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/abstract-offers-construction-continuation-sheet"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external"
                           class="- topic/xref ">OF 1419A</xref> (11/88Ed.), Abstract of Offers-Construction, Continuation Sheet</i>. OF’s <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/abstract-offers-construction"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">1419</xref> and <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/abstract-offers-construction-continuation-sheet"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">1419A</xref> are prescribed for use in recording bids (and may be used for recording proposal information), as specified in <xref href="36.701.dita#FAR_36_701"
                        base="i1078213"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">36.701</xref>(c).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
